  "_schema_version": "1.0",
  "_purpose": "Per-software-niche presets for cicd-impact calculator. Pick the closest niche, copy the inputs_yml_overrides into your inputs.yml, and run scripts/03 to recompute. The recommendations are starting points anchored to the citations in philosophy.md; override any value where you have local data that's better than the niche default.",
